## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| Post doesn't appear on website | Draft mode or `status` not set | Set both `Publish` button AND `Status` field to Published |
| Images broken on website | CMS `NEXT_PUBLIC_SERVER_URL` wrong | Must be `https://cms.emwraps.net` in production |
| Images broken locally | CMS running on wrong port | Run CMS on port 3001: `npm run dev -- --port 3001` |
| SEO fields empty | Not auto-generated | Click "Auto-generate" buttons in the SEO tab |
| Post shows wrong date | `publishedAt` not set | Set the Published At date field |
| CMS admin error about `block` type | Old Lexical format | Use `upload` type nodes, not `block` type for images |
